        <h3 class="node-title article__title--card">
            <a href="/news/academy-president-laurie-patton-announcement" rel="bookmark"><span class='field-wrapper article__title article__title--featured-news'>Announcing Laurie L. Patton as the Next President of the Academy</span></a>
        </h3>
        <div class="article__teaser article__teaser--featured-news field field-node--field-teaser-plain field-name-field-teaser-plain field-type-string-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item">Laurie L. Patton, the President of Middlebury College, has been named the next president of the American Academy of Arts &amp; Sciences. Elected to the Academy in 2018, she is a distinguished scholar of religion, an author or editor of ten books, a published poet, and a highly accomplished college and university leader. </div>
      </div>
</div>

